(46, 53, 'en', 'Mulberry Lane', 'Nguyen Duy Trinh Road, Binh Trung Dong Ward, District 2, Ho Chi Minh City', 'CVH Spring Company Limited', '<p>Strategically located along the fringe of the city centre, PARCSpring enjoys easy accessibility to Thu Thiem Tunnel and the future Ho Chi Minh City-Long Thanh-Dau Giay Highway. PARCSpring offers extensive landscaping and communal facilities within a safe environment. The apartments are designed with a functional layout to maximise living space. The project comprise 394 residential apartments across two 18-storey and one 12-storey buildings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PARCSpring offers two and three-bedroom units, furnished in earthly tones for a pleasant living atmosphere with an open kitchen concept and a practical unit layout design. Outside, a leisurely stroll along the landscaped garden on the ground floor will lead residents to a riverside park while a quick sojourn at the roof top garden will give residents a breathtaking views of surroundings and a quiet retreat away from the hustle and bustle of the urban cityscape. Other communal facilities provided within the development include a gymnasium, sheltered function area, outdoor exercise area, a multi-purpose lawn with trellis and seating, a children&rsquo;s playground and a foot reflexology path.</p>\r\n', '', 'Freehold for local Vietnamese, 50 yrs long term lease for foreigners', '<ul>\r\n	<li>50 meters lap swimming pool</li>\r\n	<li>Lake view lounge</li>\r\n	<li>Yoga deck</li>\r\n	<li>Badminton court</li>\r\n	<li>Putting green</li>\r\n	<li>Children&rsquo;s playground</li>\r\n	<li>Elderly Fitness Corner</li>\r\n	<li>Outdoor multipurpose Court</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(47, 54, 'en', 'CHÍNH CHỦ BÁN ĐẤT BIỆT THỰ LIỀN KỀ 1, LÔ 38, KĐT ĐẠI THANH', '', '', '<p>Cần b&aacute;n gấp nh&agrave; 1 trệt 1 lầu, tổng diện t&iacute;ch 90m2, Phan Văn Hớn, H&oacute;c M&ocirc;n. Gần ng&atilde; 3 Giồng. ( Cách 1,5km, chưa đ&ecirc;́n c&acirc;̀u lớn). Bao sang t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng chứng, l&agrave;m thủ tục trong ng&agrave;y, nhận nh&agrave; ngay. + Hỗ trợ vay vốn ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng l&ecirc;n tới 80%. Ai c&oacute; nhu thật sự gọi cho t&ocirc;i (Miễn tiếp m&ocirc;i giới).</p>\r\n', '', '11', '<p>TIỆN &Iacute;CH TRONG V&Ograve;NG 2KM - Nh&agrave; trường - Gym - Nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng</p>\r\n'),
