(59, 66, 'vi', 'THE VISTA AN PHÚ', 'Số 628C Xa lộ Hà Nội, phường An Phú, Quận 2, TPHCM', ' Công ty Liên doanh CapitaLand – Vista', '<p><strong>The Vista</strong>&nbsp;tọa lạc tại phường An Ph&uacute;, quận 2, Tp.HCM, nằm trong khu&ocirc;n vi&ecirc;n khoảng 2.3 hecta với vị tr&iacute; thuận lợi kết nối về trung t&acirc;m th&agrave;nh phố. The Vista c&oacute; tổng cộng 750 căn hộ cao cấp, thuộc năm t&ograve;a nh&agrave; cao 28 tầng, đều tận hưởng vẻ đẹp cảnh quan của s&ocirc;ng S&agrave;i G&ograve;n v&agrave; trung t&acirc;m th&agrave;nh phố.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Vista</strong>&nbsp;cũng c&oacute; khối đế thương mại cung cấp hơn 8.500m2 kh&ocirc;ng gian b&aacute;n lẻ với t&ecirc;n gọi The Vista Walk. Ngo&agrave;i ra, The Vista c&ograve;n c&oacute; t&ograve;a nh&agrave; Vista Tower với 100 căn hộ dịch vụ mang thương hiệu Somerset Vista v&agrave; hơn 11.000m2 kh&ocirc;ng gian văn ph&ograve;ng cho thu&ecirc;, nh&agrave; trẻ v&agrave; ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;m y tế.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista được nhận bằng khen&nbsp;<strong>The Best Development Marketing</strong>&nbsp;do&nbsp;<strong>Asia Pacific Property Awards</strong>&nbsp;trao tặng năm 2009. Bằng khen n&agrave;y l&agrave; minh chứng cho kế hoạch tiếp thị th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng trong lĩnh vực bất động sản, cho thấy The Vista đ&atilde; định vị đ&uacute;ng, cung cấp cho nhu cầu về nh&agrave; ở chất lượng cao đang ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng tăng tại Tp.HCM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista đ&atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh từ th&aacute;ng 09/2011 v&agrave; đang dần b&agrave;n giao cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n', '', 'Sở hữu vĩnh viễn đối người Việt Nam, cho thuê dài hạn (50 năm) đối với người nước ngoài', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Hồ bơi</li>\r\n	<li>Thảm cỏ tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;i</li>\r\n	<li>Ốc đảo thư gi&atilde;n</li>\r\n	<li>Vườn treo Babylon</li>\r\n	<li>S&acirc;n tập Tennis</li>\r\n	<li>S&acirc;n chơi trẻ em</li>\r\n	<li>Thư viện</li>\r\n	<li>Vườn tĩnh t&acirc;m</li>\r\n	<li>Khu BBQ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(60, 47, 'en', 'FLC COMPLEX PHAM HUNG', ' Quang Cu, Samson, Thanh Hoa province.', '	 CVH SPRING COMPANY LIMITED', '<p>It&#39;s time to pursue the perfection of life experience with the combination of residential apartments, shopping centers and services in FLC Complex Pham Hung - a real estate project of FLC Group.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nestled in a favorable location, FLC Complex Pham Hung integrates amenities with international standards, green spaces, Feng Shui energy, synchronized infrastructure, safety and apartments of all sizes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only quench your thirst for a modern living space, FLC Complex Pham Hung puts forth a combination of living and enjoying life to the fullest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Excellent location</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in a &ldquo;golden&rdquo; piece of land, FLC Complex Pham Hung borders Pham Hung street - the major route in the West of Hanoi, near two big parks and Nhan Chinh lake. The building lays among a highly intellectual population, close to elite residential accomodation and offices such as Keangnam, Indochina Plaza, The Manor, BigC Shopping center, National Convention Center, My Dinh National Stadium, and plenty of prestigious administrative headquarters, schools&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From FLC Complex Pham Hung, you can easy access to critical routes such as: The Cau Giay - Kim Ma entrance to the city central; Pham Hung street connecting the North and South of the city; Noi Bai International airport; the Ring Road No.3 interconnecting Soc Son, Tu Liem, Cau Giay,&hellip;</p>\r\n', '', 'Freehold', ''),
(61, 48, 'vi', 'KRIS VUE', 'Ngõ 543 Nguyễn Duy Trinh, District 2, Ho Chi Minh City', 'Liên doanh giữa Capitaland và Khang Điền: CapitaLand - 95% Khang Điền- 5%', '<p>Kris Vue l&agrave; dự &aacute;n nh&agrave; ở d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c gia đ&igrave;nh trẻ do c&ocirc;ng ty CapitaLand (Singapore) đầu tư v&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chỉ với 128 căn hộ được thiết kế ri&ecirc;ng tư v&agrave; mang phong c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;ch sạn cao cấp, Kris Vue mang tới cho c&aacute;c gia đ&igrave;nh trẻ giải ph&aacute;p an cư ho&agrave;n hảo với 3 loại căn hộ một + 1, hai v&agrave; ba ph&ograve;ng ngủ l&agrave; Deluxe, Executive v&agrave; Premier. Mỗi căn hộ đều được thiết kế vu&ocirc;ng vắn, tận dụng kh&ocirc;ng gian tối ưu với ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; ph&ograve;ng ăn rộng, l&ocirc;-gia tho&aacute;ng, khu vực bếp ri&ecirc;ng biệt kết nối với s&acirc;n phơi rộng r&atilde;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng chỉ t&iacute;ch hợp sự tiện lợi của c&aacute;c tiện &iacute;ch trong khu vực như chợ, si&ecirc;u thị, trường học, bệnh viện, nh&agrave; văn h&oacute;a v&agrave; c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m thương mại trong khu vực, Kris Vue c&ograve;n mang đến cho cư d&acirc;n một cuộc sống tiện nghi như tại kh&aacute;ch sạn sang trọng v&agrave; t&iacute;nh cộng đồng cao theo phong c&aacute;ch Singapore với hơn 20 loại tiện &iacute;ch v&agrave; thiết kế cảnh quan nổi bật l&agrave; hồ bơi trong nh&agrave; nước mặn, c&acirc;u lạc bộ thể thao v&agrave; yoga hiện đại, ph&ograve;ng giải tr&iacute; v&agrave; &acirc;m nhạc, sảnh đ&oacute;n sang trọng v..v..</p>\r\n', '', '', '<p>Hơn 20 tiện &iacute;ch v&agrave; t&iacute;nh năng thiết kế, bao gồm</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hồ bơi trong nh&agrave; nước mặn mang phong c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;ch sạn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hồ bơi trẻ em</li>\r\n	<li>Hồ thủy lực</li>\r\n	<li>Khu vui chơi trẻ em</li>\r\n	<li>Khu thư gi&atilde;n gia đ&igrave;nh</li>\r\n	<li>Ph&ograve;ng giải tr&iacute; &amp; &acirc;m nhạc Kris Vue</li>\r\n	<li>Ph&ograve;ng tập thể dục</li>\r\n	<li>Ph&ograve;ng yoga</li>\r\n	<li>Khu tập thể dục ngo&agrave;i trời</li>\r\n	<li>Vườn BBQ gia đ&igrave;nh</li>\r\n	<li>Sảnh đ&oacute;n sang trọng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(62, 44, 'en', 'VISTA VERDE', '628C Ha Noi Highway, An Phu Ward, Dist 2, HCMC', 'CapitaLand – Vista Joint Venture Co. Ltd', '<p>Named after &lsquo;verde&rsquo;, which means green in Spanish, Vista Verde showcases lush green landscaping and features designed to bring a symphony of nature to residents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vista Verde is strategically located in Thanh My Loi Ward, in the heart of District 2&rsquo;s administrative center. It is five minutes away from essential amenities such as Metro Hypermart, Parkson Department Store, Lotte Cinema, Phuc An Khang Hospital, and prestigious international schools such as ACG International School. Vista Verde is 10 minutes away from District 1 and 7, with excellent connectivity via the Thu Thiem Tunnel, Thu Thiem Bridge, Saigon Bridge and Phu My Bridge. The project is expected to complete towards end of 2017.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vista Verde provides residents with state-of-the-art recreational facilities such as an iconic gym and clubhouse with 360&deg; view, resort-style swimming pool, lounging islands, jogging track, and tennis court. In addition, a shopping town at the ground floor provides residents with essential retail shops their convenience. Vista Verde has over 30 unit types available in quality finishes, including special units such as duplexes and units with PES. Designed for modern living, units in Vista Verde are designed with spacious living and dining areas, natural ventilation and loggia.</p>\r\n', '', 'Freehold for local Vietnamese, 50 yrs long term lease for foreigners', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Resort-style swimming pool</li>\r\n	<li>Sky Taichi Lawn</li>\r\n	<li>Lounging Island</li>\r\n	<li>Tennis court</li>\r\n	<li>Babylon Plaza</li>\r\n	<li>Outdoor Kids Zone</li>\r\n	<li>Library</li>\r\n	<li>Harmony Garden</li>\r\n	<li>BBQ Terrace</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(63, 66, 'en', 'THE VISTA AN PHU', ' 628C Ha Noi Highway, An Phu Ward, Dist 2, HCMC', 'CapitaLand – Vista Joint Venture Co. Ltd', '<p>Located in District 2, An Phu Ward, a 2.3 hectares prime residential precinct close to the city centre, The Vista comprises 750 luxurious apartments across five 28-storey towers overlooking the Saigon River and the surrounding city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The development also comprises approximately 8,500 square metres of commercial space including a retail podium, named The Vista Walk. In addition, The Vista has Vista Tower with 100 serviced residence units under Somerset Vista and more than 11,000 square metres office space, kindergarten and health clinic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista had been awarded the Best Development Marketing award at Asia Pacific Property Awards 2009. The award recognises the successful marketing campaign for a real estate project which is positioned to meet the increasing demand for quality apartments in the city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista was successfully completed in September 2011 and has since been handed over to homebuyers.</p>\r\n', '', 'Freehold for local Vietnamese, 50 yrs long term lease for foreigners', '<ul>\r\n	<li>50 meters swimming pool</li>\r\n	<li>Water cascading features</li>\r\n	<li>Timber sun deck</li>\r\n	<li>Tennis court</li>\r\n	<li>Golf-putting green</li>\r\n	<li>Children&rsquo;s playground</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-purpose hall; gymnasium, sauna &amp; steam rooms</li>\r\n	<li>Personalized lift access system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(64, 60, 'en', 'Sunrise Garden SG4', ' 418 Quang Trung, Ha Dong, Hanoi', '', '<p>The development also comprises approximately 8,500 square metres of commercial space including a retail podium, named The Vista Walk. In addition, The Vista has Vista Tower with 100 serviced residence units under Somerset Vista and more than 11,000 square metres office space, kindergarten and health clinic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista had been awarded the Best Development Marketing award at Asia Pacific Property Awards 2009. The award recognises the successful marketing campaign for a real estate project which is positioned to meet the increasing demand for quality apartments in the city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vista was successfully completed in September 2011 and has since been handed over to homebuyers.</p>\r\n', '', 'Apartment units and Shopping Mall', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Linear design with good natural ventilation in all rooms/kitchen</li>\r\n	<li>High ceilings and spacious interior</li>\r\n	<li>Private &amp; exclusive living with only 6 &ndash; 8 units per floor</li>\r\n	<li>High quality furnishings</li>\r\n	<li>Lush greeneries all around, beautiful landscaped gardens &amp; serene water features</li>\r\n	<li>High speed passenger and service elevators</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-storey carpark</li>\r\n	<li>100% backup generator</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
